encati qui.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Nei prossimi giorni, <em>in ordine cronologico</em>, si incontrano le community di:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Torino</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 4 apr, ore 18:30, &#8220;WordPress Meetup Torino incontra gli organizzatori di WCEU 2024!&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-torino/events/300010518\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Milano</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 10 apr, ore 19:00, &#8220;Come scegliere i plugin giusti per il proprio sito WordPress&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-milano/events/300003137\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Roma</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 12 apr, ore 18:00, &#8220;Ask Me Anything About WordPress (evento modificato)&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/romawordpress/events/300033074\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Genova</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 17 apr, ore 18:30, &#8220;Data for AI&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-genova/events/300229030/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/pisa-wordpress-meetup/events/300185358/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pisa</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 17 apr, ore 19:00, &#8220;E tu come SEO?&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/pisa-wordpress-meetup/events/300185358/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/pisa-wordpress-meetup/events/300185358/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Catania</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 18 apr, ore 19:00, &#8220;WorkShop su Site Editor e temi a blocchi WordPress Me